  "texts": [
    "Our findings point to the critical need for embedding Generative AI literacy into educational curricula and to promote critical thinking abilities among students.",
    "Looking ahead, our research suggests integrating LLM-powered tools in computer science education requires more tools, resources, and regulations to help students develop Generative AI literacy and customize teaching strategies to bridge the gap between tool capabilities and educational goals.",
